Antclone web application
=============================

REQUIREMENTS:

Database
-----------------------------
PostgreSQL 9.1 + PostGIS extension.

Web server
-----------------------------
Tomcat 7.0

Build system
-----------------------------
Maven


INSTALLATION HISTORY for h2.yatko.com:

1) Installed jdk 1.7 as described in http://www.if-not-true-then-false.com/2010/install-sun-oracle-java-jdk-jre-7-on-fedora-centos-red-hat-rhel/
2) Updated JAVA_HOME in /etc/bashrc
3) Installed Java Cryptography Extension from http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jce-7-download-432124.html
4) Installed tomcat 7 into /usr/share/apache-tomcat-7.0.29
5) Created startup script /etc/init.d/tomcat
6) Installed PostreSQL 9.1 following this guide http://www.davidghedini.com/pg/entry/install_postgresql_9_on_centos
7) Installed PostGIS 2 following this guide http://www.davidghedini.com/pg/tags/postgis


